1. download pyinstaller
http://www.pyinstaller.org/downloads.html

2. 执行pyinstaller *.py报错：Python library not found: libpython3.6.so.1.0, libpython3.6m.so.1.0, libpython3.6mu.so.1.0
需要执行export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/home/allen/anaconda3/lib


-------------------------------------------------------------
1. python -m py_compile *.py
//生成*.pyc文件

